OL,3,CInside Jersey's new acute adult mental
OL,4,Chealth facility
OL,6,FA new inpatient mental health centre
OL,7,Fwill start welcoming Jersey patients
OL,8,Ffrom next week.
OL,10,FThe 16-bed Clinique Pinel will open
OL,11,Fits doors to patients transferring
OL,12,Ffrom Orchard House on Thursday 27 June.
OL,14,FConstruction began at Clinique Pinel
OL,15,Fin 2020, as part of a refurbishment
OL,16,Fproject alongside the existing Orchard
OL,17,FHouse and Rosewood House.
