OL,3,CInside Jersey's new acute adult mental
OL,4,Chealth facility
OL,6,FThe total project was originally
OL,7,Fslated to cost almost #8.2m, however,
OL,8,Fthe final estimated cost is around
OL,9,F#10.7m due to additional upgrading
OL,10,Fworks.
OL,12,FHealth Minister Deputy Tom Binet says
OL,13,Fit is a "long time coming", adding it
OL,14,Fis a "big improvement" compared to
OL,15,FOrchard House.
OL,17,FClinique Pinel currently consists of
OL,18,F16 en-suite operational beds, but
OL,19,Fofficials say the number can be
OL,20,Fincreased if demand for mental health
OL,21,Fservices in Jersey rises.
