OL,3,CInside Jersey's new acute adult mental
OL,4,Chealth facility
OL,6,FThe intensive care unit is larger than
OL,7,FOrchard Houses' so patients can be
OL,8,Fnursed safely and separately, with a
OL,9,Fseparate assessment area for those
OL,10,Fdetained by police.
OL,12,FIn July, Clinique Pinel staff will
OL,13,Fwork with police on a joint training
OL,14,Fprogramme to understand how to best
OL,15,Fsupport individuals with mental health
OL,16,Fneeds.
OL,18,FThe new facility will also contain
OL,19,Fwomen-only and men-only places, with a
OL,20,Fspecial ward designed for those aged
OL,21,Fover 65.
