OL,4,Chealth facility
OL,6,FGarden spaces for flowers and growing
OL,7,Fvegetables have also been created,
OL,8,Fwith an external garden space to
OL,9,Ffollow once additional planning
OL,10,Fpermission is secured.
OL,12,FDirector of Mental Health and Adult
OL,13,FSocial Care, Andy Weir, said: "It's
OL,14,Fgoing to be better in a number of ways.
OL,16,F"I think it's brighter, it feels more
OL,17,Ftherapeutic, and it gives an
OL,18,Fopportunity for some activities that
OL,19,Fwe can't deliver in Orchard House."
